name: Welcome!
body:
# Welcome to my GitHub Pages.

Here are some projects that I think that somebody out there might find useful.

## [Tax Worksheets](https://ewcole.github.io/tax_worksheets)

These are Excel spreadsheets that I use to figure out my taxes each year.  Generally, this project will include the ones that are useful to me.

## [Wizard Clocks](https://ewcole.github.io/wizardclocks)

Wizard Clocks is a place where I put a few designs I made for my own enjoyment.  Currently, I have an embeddable [pregnancy timeline widget](https://ewcole.github.io/wizardclocks/pregnancy/planeTimeline), which I dusted off to prepare for my [new baby girl](https://ewcole.github.io/wizardclocks/pregnancy/planeTimeline/pregnancyTimeline.html)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
